8. **搜索数组（线性搜索和二分搜索）**
   - **线性搜索示例代码**
   ```java
   public class LinearSearch {
       public static int linearSearch(int[] list, int key) {
           for (int i = 0; i < list.length; i++) {
               if (list[i] == key) {
                   return i;
               }
           }
           return -1;
       }
   }
